FBIS3-7651 "dreas061_d_94019" FBIS-EAS-94-061 Document Type:Daily Report 27 Mar 1994 South Korea DPRK Said To Upgrade Najin-Sonbong Trade Zone SK2703051494 Seoul TONG-A ILBO in Korean 27 Mar 94 p 2 SK2703051494 Seoul TONG-A ILBO Language: Korean Article Type:BFN [From NAEWOE News Agency] [Text] It has been learned that North Korea has upgraded Najin-Sonbong area -- which was developed into a free economic trade zone in December 1991 -- into a direct-supervision city. The free economic trade zone, which has an area of 621 square km, will include some part of Undok County near the zone. As a result, the trade zone will have a total area of 764 square km.
